entry.string: echo "Node.js version:" node --version echo "NPM version:" npm --version echo "Docker version:" docker --version
echo "Running ESLint..." npx eslint . --ext .js,.jsx,.ts,.tsx --format compact || true echo "Code analysis completed"
echo "Running Jest tests..." npm test -- --coverage --watchAll=false || true echo "Unit tests completed"

docker build -t registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/hanchanglin/tbk:10-262005a . docker tag registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/hanchanglin/tbk:10-262005a registry.cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/hanchanglin/tbk:latest echo "Docker image built successfully"
docker system prune -f --volumes || true echo "Cleanup completed"
